                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e7">
                           <desc>- Words or lines have been blotted out: <locus target="#10v">10v</locus>, 20r, 29v, 33v, 115v, 118r, 136r.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e8">
                           <desc> - Erasures marked
                           with thin lines: e.g., <locus target="#24r">24r</locus>, 59v, 64r, 71v,
                                          89r, 101v, 111v, 132r, 141va, 146rb, 148rb, 150rb.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e9">
                           <desc> - Pen trial:
                                             <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>. </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e10">
                           <desc> - Crude notes, doodles: <locus target="#1rv">1rv</locus>, 152v.</desc>
                        </item>
